Rating: 4
A gorgeous salad. The best version I've had in a restaurant is at Bouchon in Las Vegas (chef Thomas Keller of French Laundry). I've been trying to replicate it and this gets close! One tip& toss the salad and the dressing in a bowl to coat it well, then shake off excess and transfer to plates. Do NOT let the vinegar pool at the bottom of the plate; once the egg breaks over it it'll be a mess if you do.

